Besides landing the Super Bowl 's halftime show and scoring the second most watched spot to launching her Joanne world tour, she must be on top of the world! 
And lucky for the songstress, she has a new man to celebrate all these happy developments with!

It's been revealed by People on Thursday that the New York native is dating her CAA talent agent Christian Carino ! 
The two were seen putting on some PDA during Sunday's Super Bowl, looking very much like a couple. Ooh la la! 
As you probably recall, GaGa was engaged to Taylor Kinney , but the two broke up this past July. It's been rumored her ex has since moved onâ€¦ and now so has she! 
Except it doesn't sound like she's completely ready to open up about it, judging by her Thursday interview with Ryan Seacrest ! When asked if she had a special man , the 30-year-old blushed, saying: 
"I don't know. You know I don't talk about my love life, Ryan! I'm really red. I'm really red and it doesn't go with my outfit."
